fields.title: Cat Quest
fields.synopsis: While out at sea, the hero of our tale, who will be referred to as 'Hero', watched as his beloved sister is kidnapped by a villainous white cat. Shipwrecked, and in a continent beset by dragons, Hero learns he is capable of slaying the monsters. He and his guardian spirit, Spirry, set out on a mission from Drakoth, the white cat from before, to get stronger and defeat the monstrous dragons (which he summoned) currently plaguing the continent. Only then will Hero and his sister be reunited...

fields.title: Cat Quest II
fields.synopsis: Having finally returned to life after dying, two kings, a cat and a dog, find that their former kingdoms have fallen into corrupt hands and are at the brink of war. The two kings and their royal advisor set out on a quest to save their world from a genuine cat-astrophe. Aided by the armorer, Kit Cat, and weapons master,  Hotto Doggo, the kings must liberate their subjects and stop the imminent war between their kingdoms.
